OL,14,Ftaking drugs. I found out when she was
OL,15,F17 that she had started using heroin.
OL,17,F"Right up until her death, she had
OL,18,Fattempted several times to come off
OL,19,Fdrugs with the help of family, support
OL,20,Fworkers and Extern."
